///////////////////
Angular
> Angular is a frontend framework which help to build
single page application using component structure

npm > Node Package manager
///////////////////////
JSON > JavaScript Object Notation
Way to Represent Data
[
    {
        "name":"Amit",
        "city":"Mumbai",
        "age":11
    },
    {
        "name":"Nikita",
        "city":"Paris"
    }
]
///////Package.json///////
> Entry point to app
> Meta data (name,version,description)
> Package used in app
> Commands(start,build,test)

////Step to generate package.json////////
**NodeJs must be install in laptop
> open cmd/terminal and go inside folder
> npm init
> answer all questions
> type 'yes'

///setup Angular App////
//Windows
# one time for each laptop
> open the cmd as adminstrator
> npm i -g @angular/cli
> close cmd

# next every time you need new app
> open cmd
> go inside folder using cmd
> ng new appname

//Mac/linux
# one time for each laptop
> open the terminal
> sudo npm i -g @angular/cli
> close terminal

# next every time you need new app
> open terminal
> go inside folder using terminal
> ng new appname


//////Step to Run App/////////
> open cmd
> go inside the folder of app
> npm start

////////////////////////////////////

package-lock > dependency tree
.gitignore> what not pushh to git
node_modules > where all package available
Readme.md(mark down) > Detail description of app
tsconfig.json > this file have configuration to convert back in Js
tsconfig.app.js > this file help to complie the application
karma > help for testing configuration
.editorconfig > Make same standard for all developer
.browserslistrc> browser version and compatibility
angular.json > this is the first file to run the app after package.json
            > Any common css/js add here
            > which is first file for .ts and .html as well
Src
style.css > common css for the app
polyfills > to make app compatibility with IE
main.ts > which is the main module
index.html > this is the main html file
            > afte complie all app will come inside this file
            > first file pick by browser


////Building Block of Angular////
Modules (NgModule)
    > Here all the declaration happen
    > Parent of the app
Component (component)
    > Html, css ,logics
Pipes (pipe,pipetranform)
    > Filter the data
    > Run time data manipulation
Service (Injectable)
    > Dependency Injection
    > To connect with external agent
Routing (NgModule)
    > To Jump between the pages


